Metadata-Version: 1.2
Name: fusus
Version: 0.0.2
Summary: Workflow for converting Arabic scanned pages into readable text
Home-page: https://github.com/among/fusus
Author: Cornelis van Lit, Dirk Roorda
Author-email: dirk.roorda@dans.knaw.nl
License: UNKNOWN
Description: Workflow from scanned pages of Arabic Medieval books to readable text.
        With cleaning before OCR, OCR itself, and postprocessing.
        Tools to read text corpora with (linguistic) annotations
        and process them efficiently.
        With a built in web-interface for querying a corpus.
        More info on https://among.github.io/fusus/
        
